{"title":"希望","authors":["晨梅"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":6,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨梅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的童年和少年时代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空灰蒙蒙，乌云遮着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日月星辰的灿烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的童年和少年时代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像断线的风筝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂飙中已飘逝很远很远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倘有第二次生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿是春天的小白杨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踮起脚尖去亲吻蓝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——回报大地母亲的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养育之恩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今的孩子像葵花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细雨艳阳下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开放着天真与烂漫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光如此明媚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花儿这般金灿，皆因"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由地舒展"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记住这旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是毛主席1949年10月1日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天安门广场亲手升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这旗，凝聚着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老一辈无产阶级革命家的智慧和血汗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这旗，是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千千万万革命先烈的热血染红！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论在天涯海角，无论"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进的路多么坎坷泥泞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心灵的天空务必时刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高扬着五星红旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边风光真好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记住是谁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤来浩荡的春风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱散了我们头顶的沉沉乌云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来改革开放的缤纷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类的发展没有穷尽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华腾飞仗群才"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青少年是祖国的栋梁和希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们一定会托起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世纪的太阳！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}